# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local Privy (development)
#
# SETUP: Copy this file to:  frontend/.env.development.local
#        (.env.development.local is gitignored — never commit real values.)
#
# Paste VITE_PRIVY_* from Vercel → Environment Variables or Privy Dashboard.
# App URL: http://localhost:8080  |  Restart `npm run dev` after saving.
